title: Former La Jolla Music Society finance director pleads guilty to embezzlement - La Jolla Light
content: Former La Jolla Music Society finance director pleads guilty to embezzlement  La Jolla Light
description: Chris Benavides, former longtime director of finance for the La Jolla Music Society, pleaded guilty Feb. 23 in federal court to embezzling more than $650,000 over a decade.
